{"data":[{"id":562806887,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"276fa0bc5305193ab096781d0e4844ef","url_token":"luo-da-you-99","name":"尽黑丶","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7739b5ebd3ed72ce997d2557d1e494ea_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-7739b5ebd3ed72ce997d2557d1e494ea_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/276fa0bc5305193ab096781d0e4844ef","user_type":"people","headline":"自闭","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":486,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562806887","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1ffadb5643200823ec549fd0d0966ca1_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546148377,"updated_time":1546148967,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e以前学了一个伪算法\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e简单的某问题P0\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果一个正整数数是偶数将其除以2，如果一个数是奇数将其乘3-1问是不是最终该算法能得到1\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e是的，似乎这个问题写成代码它总是能得到2^n然后得到2得到1\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是你问存不存在一个反例使它永远得不到？这个问题目前无法解决。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实筛法的局限性就是实在无限和潜在无限的区别。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我小学的时候就思考过：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e随着正整数N增大，N的可组合因子数越来越多，从中凑出素数解的期望也越来越大。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7e72095d227f1932da0c942e2756e2a9_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"500\" data-rawheight=\"329\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d51904f73946c4cb65f09396e9750364_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"500\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7e72095d227f1932da0c942e2756e2a9_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='500'%20height='329'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"500\" data-rawheight=\"329\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d51904f73946c4cb65f09396e9750364_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"500\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7e72095d227f1932da0c942e2756e2a9_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-7e72095d227f1932da0c942e2756e2a9_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e这就像你问给定m=1/10\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ep1为0的概率为1-m\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ep2为0的概率为1-m^2\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003epn为0的概率为1-m^n\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e假如你验证了p1p2p3...p10都不是0\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那么我问你\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e （连乘）∏pn是不是0\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你只知道这件事发生的概率越来越小以至于没法举出反例，但是实际上你永远没办法说反例不存在。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以我感觉其实哥猜只是概率无限命题P的一种表述\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e如果p发生的概率随着观测越来越小，那么p会发生吗？请证明p会发生或证明p不会发生\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e显然地，p-\u0026gt;0不代表p是不可能事件\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我相信反例是存在的，也即哥猜不成立，只不过这个数过大，大概有1/p^实无限大 位，人类找不到罢了。但是，相比真正的潜无限大，这个数还是存在的。你可能会问我数学家给出存在性证明不就好了吗，不过很容易理解的是，对于某些问题，给出存在性证明本身就是在找反例，所以数学方法给不出实无限大数N0的存在性也是可能的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你如果观察一下前面的3n-1问题，再观察一下哥猜，其实道理很简单，我们的公理体系对某些问题，只能从概率意义上解决问题，既不能证明它是对的，也不能证明它是错的，这和我们采用的的证明工具无关。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以我以前听高中老师说“哥猜用初等数学手段无法证明”，我当时想当然如此，因为这类概率意义问题本身就和严格证明相悖。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以题主还是好好准备高考吧\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"以前学了一个伪算法 简单的某问题P0 如果一个正整数数是偶数将其除以2，如果一个数是奇数将其乘3-1问是不是最终该算法能得到1 是的，似乎这个问题写成代码它总是能得到2^n然后得到2得到1 但是你问存不存在一个反例使它永远得不到？这个问题目前无法解决。 …","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=529\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_t